持[[智利護照|智利護照]]的{{link-en|智利人口|Demographics of Chile|智利公民}}公民可以免簽入境新加坡30天<ref name="visapol">{{cite web|title = Visa Requirements|url = http://www.ica.gov.sg/page.aspx?pageid=96|work = ICA|accessdate = 2013-12-17|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131225214257/http://www.ica.gov.sg/page.aspx?pageid=96|archivedate = 2013年12月25日}}</ref><ref name="tim">{{Timatic Visa Policy|country=SG|=1 April 2017}}</ref>，但護照有效期需在6个月以上，並需出示续程或回程的機票等。<ref name="entry">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ica.gov.sg/page.aspx?pageid=95#yellowfever|title=Entry Requirements|access-date=2017-07-31|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731155413/https://www.ica.gov.sg/page.aspx?pageid=95#yellowfever|archivedate=2017-07-31}}</ref>

